name: Whiphid
Lore: 'Whipids originate from Toola in the Kaelta system, a planet extremely distant from its sun. Accustomed to hunting for prey in the near dark and the bitter cold.',
Text: 'Power +2 on Hoth. Forfeit +2 under nighttime conditions. When at a site, if opponent cancels Sunsdown at the related system, causes Effect to go to Used Pile, and you may retrieve 2 Force.',
